{
  "analytics_identifier": null,
  "base_path": "/expenses-and-benefits-lost-time-payments",
  "content_id": "ef8b8857-1390-40b3-8df2-de7f48e3a143",
  "description": "Tax and reporting rules for employers providing payments to cover loss of earnings",
  "details": {
    "external_related_links": [

    ],
    "hide_chapter_navigation": false,
    "parts": [
      {
        "body": "<p>As an employer, you have certain tax, National Insurance and reporting obligations if you make lost-time payments to employees who attend third-party events.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"whats-included\">What’s included</h2>\n\n<p>Events covered by lost-time payments include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>trade union meetings</li>\n  <li>meetings of public bodies</li>\n  <li>jury service</li>\n</ul>\n",
        "slug": "overview",
        "title": "Overview"
      },
      {
        "body": "<p>If the lost-time payment only replaces an employee’s lost earnings, you don’t have to report anything to <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> or pay tax and National Insurance.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"jury-service\">Jury service</h2>\n\n<p>You don’t have to <a href=\"/giving-staff-time-off-jury-service/paying-staff-on-jury-service\">pay staff while they’re doing jury service</a>, but many employers do.</p>\n\n<p>If you don’t pay them, they can claim a loss of earnings allowance from the court.</p>\n\n",
        "slug": "whats-exempt",
        "title": "What's exempt"
      },
      {
        "body": "<p>If the lost-time payment is more than an employee’s lost earnings, you must:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>add this extra amount to your employee’s earnings</li>\n  <li>deduct and pay Class 1 National Insurance and <abbr title=\"Pay As You Earn\">PAYE</abbr> tax through payroll</li>\n</ul>\n\n",
        "slug": "what-to-report-and-pay",
        "title": "What to report and pay"
      },
      {
        "body": "<p>The following guides contain more detailed information:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/manuals/eimanual/eim01120.htm\" title=\"EIM01120: Employment income - financial loss allowances\">employment income: financial loss allowances</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/manuals/nimmanual/nim02220.htm\" title=\"NIM02220: Class 1 NICs - lost-time payments\">Class 1 National Insurance: lost-time payments</a></p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n",
        "slug": "technical-guidance",
        "title": "Technical guidance"
      }
    ]
  },
